{
  "stem": "13690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not ask him-- they just told him, 'You're wearing fur pants, which they're supposed to have been delivered.' They killed him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they did in a very humiliating way-- they gave ordinance, if you give so much and so much contribution of money, we will let you be free.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, free in a sense we will not bother you that you should give so many so many men for work, or so many, many more restrictions, or you get more rations.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't forget, we-- all-- all the food, whatever meager part, was given to us by rations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, we had little pieces of paper for rations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the contributions that-- that we had to give or, so to say, to be bailed out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say this town population-- let's say 4,000 Jews-- had to deliver by the date so-and-so-- has to deliver, let's say, 1 million [? zloty, ?] or 100,000, or whatever amount.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that date, that money had to be delivered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People were given rations, to-- to-- that they could get, let's say, a pound or two pounds of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do not recall the exactly weigh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I definitely did not go to pick up my-- my portion or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say they were giving--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say they were registered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not have any ID card whatsoever throughout my time, being, during the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were helping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My home, that I was brought up, that we always helped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we were fortunate to have certain reserves of money that we could help people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I do remember at the time that 300 Jews were put into our town from-- were expelled from the north into our town.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
